{"tid":1135404,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【安心餘波】網民促無綫炒黃心穎 黃心妙：我們活在語言暴力年代","createTime":"2019-05-02T09:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T21:31:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":29,"dislike":336,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"8960bc802cd09e37e722b0e71979872a636a218b","tid":1135404,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T09:41:14.000Z","msg":"黃心穎上月受「安心事件」影響，一直由家姐輪流照顧，有傳心穎當時秘密前往澳門，投靠嫁給澳門商人的二家姐黃心妙，之後由澳門飛去菲律賓，再轉機往美國，目前在美國進修，重新生活，怎料今日爆出網民發起「要求無綫與黃心穎即時終止經理人合約」萬人聯署行動，直至今午4時已有逾1,600人簽署。<br />\n心穎早前忽然閂IG留言功能，網民在大家姐心美及二家姐心妙的IG洗版罵心穎，心妙今日在IG留言，稱活在一個充滿語言暴力的年代：「很多人都認為他們可以做這種精神上和心理上侵犯別人的行為，大家都化身為判官，選擇以暴易暴，我們的世界真的生病了，世界上有很多的戰爭，太多的生老病死，在死亡面前我們甚麼都不是，看淡了就可以坦然面對一切，快樂的時候留一點空間給悲傷，悲傷的時候留一點空間給快樂進來。」<br />\n心妙又指做錯了應自己去承擔及改過，成長路還很長，作為一個女兒、妹妹、姐姐、媽媽、妻子、朋友及過客：「幸運的我可以擁有不同的經歷和閱歷，能夠不斷的反思和進步，每個人生活都不容易，笑臉我會一直掛上，用我的方式，主宰自己的生活，感謝一路相伴的你們」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190502/large/1556783335_a1b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190502%2Flarge%2F1556783335_a1b9.jpg&h=45ab80b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190502/large/1556784434_9469.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190502%2Flarge%2F1556784434_9469.jpg&h=f52f4902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190502/59554933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190502%2F59554933&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJuwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=95dd98cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190502%2F59554933&h=bb810c16\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190502/59554933</a>"},{"pid":"b2725950bb6300e77851176624de8a4a286a1452","tid":1135404,"uid":65371,"like":342,"dislike":1,"score":341,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T09:42:52.000Z","msg":"請不要轉發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆街蘋果又助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d559f9defb58340d5dc257e0d2ee1b0ca9f93a","tid":1135404,"uid":31525,"like":343,"dislike":4,"score":339,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T09:43:59.000Z","msg":"睇錯黃心炒"},{"pid":"82efdd05a2180cd5bc134e915d7ff33a6bc638f1","tid":1135404,"uid":4525,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T09:44:18.000Z","msg":"投共禁聲<br />\n安心偷食"},{"pid":"b1598b79c6bcda8a312687c828125fa5fc807e06","tid":1135404,"uid":217336,"like":444,"dislike":15,"score":429,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T09:47:15.000Z","msg":"做得公眾人物就預左<br />\n你做得好時接受公眾欣賞讚美時又會唔會話我地係判官？"},{"pid":"3df9c2e82e58d3c1db4881a9cf1cbb879907b857","tid":1135404,"uid":236359,"like":31,"dislike":102,"score":-71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T10:13:41.000Z","msg":"香港網民一向出名惡過狗"},{"pid":"7e3a1783cc01d6d25734ffc8b62d6287db72d484","tid":1135404,"uid":180404,"like":397,"dislike":19,"score":378,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T10:15:53.000Z","msg":"偷食被發現,仲好意思講語言暴力XD<br />\n<br />\n唔知要幾厚面皮先講得出口"},{"pid":"196413344776b00495c3941fc54a51accbfdb2f4","tid":1135404,"uid":2545,"like":23,"dislike":39,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"7e3a1783cc01d6d25734ffc8b62d6287db72d484","tid":1135404,"uid":180404,"like":397,"dislike":19,"score":378,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T10:15:53.000Z","msg":"偷食被發現,仲好意思講語言暴力XD<br />\n<br />\n唔知要幾厚面皮先講得出口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T10:17:44.000Z","msg":"係囉XDXDXDXDXD"},{"pid":"1c43f34ba9213fe51f6e903e6fa4e0e65a3f7f55","tid":1135404,"uid":55519,"like":145,"dislike":1,"score":144,"quote":{"pid":"7e3a1783cc01d6d25734ffc8b62d6287db72d484","tid":1135404,"uid":180404,"like":397,"dislike":19,"score":378,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T10:15:53.000Z","msg":"偷食被發現,仲好意思講語言暴力XD<br />\n<br />\n唔知要幾厚面皮先講得出口"},"citedBy":0,